sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant D as Streamlit Dashboard
    participant A as FastAPI /predict
    participant R as ModelRegistry
    participant IF as Isolation Forest
    participant L as LSTM Autoencoder
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant W as Discord Webhook

    User->>D: Select series & request scoring
    D->>A: POST /predict {window, series_key}
    A->>R: get_scaler(series_key)
    R-->>A: fitted MinMax scaler
    A->>A: scale window, extract 8 features
    A->>IF: score(features)
    IF-->>A: anomaly score + flag
    A->>L: score(window_3d)
    L-->>A: reconstruction error + flag
    A->>A: combine (union / intersection)
    alt anomaly detected (union)
        A->>DB: log_prediction(...)
        A->>W: fire_alert() if cooldown elapsed
        A->>DB: log_alert(prediction_id, sent)
    end
    A-->>D: PredictResponse {flags, scores, alert_sent}
    D-->>User: Render anomaly markers on chart
